{"tid":1762382,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"10 月訪港旅客量較去年同期續跌　中國遊客大減 46%","createTime":"2019-11-29T14:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T14:33:52.000Z","uid":41404,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b125009b014098aea14d32286c9b5d5b869b2356","tid":1762382,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T14:24:03.000Z","msg":"旅發局今日公布最新數字，顯示上月份整體訪港旅客量由去年同期 588 萬人次銳減至 331 萬人次，跌幅達 43.7%，是 5 個月來最大跌幅。其中內地訪港旅客人次更大跌 45.9%，由去年同期 465 萬人次減至 251 萬人次。<br />\n<br />\n至於非內地旅客亦錄得 35.6% 跌幅，訪港人次由 123 萬跌至 79 萬。<br />\n<br />\n短途地區市場的災情嚴重，訪港人次跌 43.5%，由去年同期63萬人次跌至 35萬人次；長途地區市場跌幅則只有 27.7%，由去年同期 44萬人次跌至 32萬人次。以地區劃分，泰國是所有地區中錄得最大跌幅，訪港人次大減 60.2%，只有 1.6 萬人次來港，其次包括越南、南韓、新加坡、日本等地。<br />\n<br />\n過夜旅客人次同樣大跌，總過夜旅客人次由 253 萬跌至 136 萬，大減 46.1%；其中內地客訪港人次跌 48.1%至 90萬人次；短途客及長途客則分別跌 50.8%及 31.5%。"},{"pid":"0863698542959d9fe3cf0db6d4c6759df1400fa1","tid":1762382,"uid":40439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T14:25:11.000Z","msg":"仲有90萬人次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b298640941d83fd0e65ea62f14a96f58b8a0fb21","tid":1762382,"uid":25538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0863698542959d9fe3cf0db6d4c6759df1400fa1","tid":1762382,"uid":40439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T14:25:11.000Z","msg":"仲有90萬人次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T14:27:33.000Z","msg":"跌果少少又話失業乜乜柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f20c2e2fb40c077f1d6c79f7a24f2cc3b07290","tid":1762382,"uid":207902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T14:28:16.000Z","msg":"沒有支那人的香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8cc54002becc